---
description: Traveler flow guidance for demand-side work
globs:
  - "src/app/(protected)/traveler/**"
  - "src/features/traveler/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Traveler scope is request creation, joining, bookings, favorites, and traveler account UX.
- Keep traveler-specific logic in `src/features/traveler`.
- Shared contracts and backend shapes belong in the data layer, not page-local code.
